Building from source on Debian/Ubuntu

1. Make sure you have build tools installed:
 $ apt-get install build-essential debhelper xsltproc docbook-xml docbook-xsl python-all

2. Install a few python modules
 $ apt-get install python-feedparser python-beautifulsoup python-zope python-imaging python-oauth2client python-googleapi python-suds python-requests-oauthlib python-oauthlib python-requests python-blinker python-jwt python-urllib3

3. Clone the git repo
 $ git clone https://forja.cenatic.es/anonscm/git/iteexe/iteexe.git
 
4. cd to this directory and run the make process
 $ cd <checkoutdir>/iteexe/installs/debian/ubuntu
 $ python make.py
 

